main takeaway is, while I have some questions, it would be my preference not to just like provide a laundry list today, you know, I don't have any questions that are going to be so unexpected that I think, you know, withholding them would somehow, you know, hurt the proponent or anything like that, you know, they're going to be very much so in the wheelhouse of these core areas.

